snippet.title: Combines.io [Farmers.io] INSTANT WIN! Map Control: 100%
snippet.description: Try to be the leader of the match and make other combines crash in order to pick up all their harvest and increase your score. The more you collect, the larger you will become, so keep going until you have become a huge truck that destroys everyone else. Complete achievements and have fun playing Combines.io!
